{"tid":1726804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【政府埋單】全民申請老綜！","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:58:35.000Z","uid":6980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8beceaa92530953d259c13b767817bbdf6c486","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"尋日睇完呢個post諗到啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">基層工種將出現大裁員 藍絲好快全線收皮 我地將會揸住經濟大春袋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n班藍屍成日話示威搞到佢哋手停口停<br />\n我哋把握機會，將個波推返俾政府<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>場運動係政府搞出嚟，應該搵政府埋單</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇工開嗰班基層市民，請立即申請綜援，要求政府賠償！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔止藍屍<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人應該不分黃藍，全民申請老綜</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npps交稅都逐蚊交<br />\n試諗下全民咬老綜<br />\n申請成功固然可以陰乾政府庫房<br />\n唔成功都可以加重社署paper work<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當有10萬人申請，逐個審查都咪話唔和味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a635eba1c4625f9c1d1a7f20b4f13259dd2790","tid":1726804,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f68e713e2d9bc783de10028778e6c66df75df97","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21db67ec7739eaf22d8f3126a48e9413a2c8f5d7","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"美心都快啲向政府索償啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46198b711e85db7569acdc8d06a26da541baadae","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"所有被裝修店舖都要向政府索償<br />\n示威者冇大台，冇得追我哋數<br />\n但紅藍屍個大台就係政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民追政府數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4d1b3ecdc6c1552a25c2d9c69ddd2e931c962f","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"全民咬老綜不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc16564a872cb88969bf66af983c954227d5e9","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"示威者搞到我冇工開<br />\n政府好快啲賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc7b17858f9dd745656300c79e17b99ff8706b9","tid":1726804,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"正有此意！！"},{"pid":"00b330d30035f2ae95d365a714da0ca974e22af8","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"伍小姐唔好放棄政府呀<br />\n你好大條數要追架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb30a8895182af21cd3389bccad746bc87e0a57","tid":1726804,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"85265f717d402ec6ad87e0dca5e9ed84cbe60845","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"福建360都係<br />\n申請唔到老綜，都唔可以俾政府走數！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579eecab67feef0efadece190659f5d28d63fe6a","tid":1726804,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"讚成 ， 攞政府錢，同時減少稅收"},{"pid":"f168c319248eb63da6128b8415ec89edf4321cd0","tid":1726804,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"還富於民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b616f1b585379898130c860f3c70c924660c17","tid":1726804,"uid":235119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"tui"}]}